prod_short_desc: Load up the Cargo Plane and get ready to fly!
prod_long_desc:
Get the LEGO® City Airport Cargo Plane ready for delivery, featuring a back hatch that opens, turning nosewheel, big engines and accessible cockpit, plus an airport service car with hand truck and space for 4 packages. Includes 2 minifigures.
Build a sturdy cargo plane, featuring an opening back hatch for loading and deliveries, big engines and accessible cockpit, plus an airport service car!
Includes a pilot and an airport worker
LEGO City building toys are compatible with all LEGO construction sets for creative building
Cargo Plane measures over 3” high, 9” long and 10” wide. Airport service car measures over 1” high, 2” long and 1” wide
157 pieces – For boys and girls between the ages of 5 and 12
